00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Seth-Rogen-James-Franco-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Seth-Rogen-James-Franco-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Seth-Rogen-James-Franco-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Seth-Rogen-James-Franco-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Seth-Rogen-James-Franco-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seth-rogen">Seth Rogen</a> didn&#39;t pay attention to the reaction online after <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-franco">James Franco</a> shared that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-franco-says-friendship-with-seth-rogen-is-over-3806443">their friendship was over</a> last year, he&#39;s revealed.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/seth-rogen-movies-10-best-2724501">Riding high: Seth Rogen&#39;s 10 best films</a></strong></li></ul><p> The actor told <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/article/seth-rogen-on-fame-smoking-weed-and-why-his-films-have-not-aged-well-ksm8pvtvl" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Sunday Times</em></a> in 2021 that he wasn&#39;t planning on working with his former friend and collaborator Franco again after <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/james-franco-sexual-misconduct-accusations-2216394">sexual misconduct allegations were made against the latter</a> .</p><p> Franco told <a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/global/james-franco-new-movie-hey-joe-lawsuit-seth-rogen-friendship-1236190559/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> last year, “No. I haven&#39;t talked to Seth. I love Seth, we had 20 great years together, but I guess it&#39;s over. And not for lack of trying. I&#39;ve told him how much he&#39;s meant to me.”</p><p> When asked by <em><a href="https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/tv/a63613027/seth-rogen-interview-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Esquire</a></em> how it felt “to have something so personal become so public,” Rogen was hesitant to discuss it, saying, “Honestly, I absorb so little media that it really wasn&#39;t on my radar.”</p><p> Rogen and Franco first gained attention in the late 1990s on NBC&#39;s cult teen high school comedy-drama <em>Freaks And Geeks</em> , before then starring alongside each other in the 2007 rom-com <em>Knocked Up</em> . Over the next decade, they worked together in comedies including <em>Pineapple Express</em> and <em>This Is The End</em> , with their last movie together being 2017&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/disaster-artist-film-review-2168667"><em>The Disaster Artist</em></a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3837161" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837161" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837161" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018.jpg" alt="James Franco and Seth Rogen celebrate The 75th Annual Golden Globe Awards with Moet &amp; Chandon at The Beverly Hilton Hotel on January 7, 2018 in Beverly Hills, California" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Franco-Rogen-2018-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837161" class="wp-caption-text"> James Franco and Seth Rogen celebrate The 75th Annual Golden Globe Awards with Moet &amp; Chandon at The Beverly Hilton Hotel on January 7, 2018 in Beverly Hills, California. CREDIT: Michael Kovac/Getty Images for Moet &amp; Chandon</figcaption></figure><p> In 2018, Franco was accused of sexual misconduct, with an attorney for Franco denying the allegations at the time. In February 2021, Franco <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-franco-sexual-misconduct-lawsuit-reaches-settlement-deal-2885100">settled a lawsuit with two of the women who&#39;d accused him</a> , and per records from the Los Angeles Superior Court, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-franco-agrees-to-pay-2-2m-settlement-for-sexual-misconduct-suit-2982786">he agreed to pay $2,235,000</a> (around £1,700,000).</p><p> They claimed that he&#39;d pushed his acting students to perform explicit scenes on camera, while the lawsuit also alleged that Franco and his partners “engaged in widespread inappropriate and sexually charged behaviour towards female students by sexualising their power as a teacher and an employer by dangling the opportunity for roles in their projects.”</p><p> Though Rogen originally said he&#39;d continue working with Franco after the allegations came out, he said otherwise in his <em>Sunday Times</em> interview. He said at the time: “I also look back to that interview in 2018 where I comment that I would keep working with James, and the truth is that I have not and I do not plan to right now,” while he added that the allegations “changed many things in our relationship and our dynamic.”</p><p> When the newspaper suggested that the situation must have been painful for him, he said: “Yeah. But not as painful and difficult as it is for a lot of other people involved. I have no pity for myself in this situation.”</p><p> Rogen&#39;s new comedy series, meanwhile, is set to hit <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a> next month. The first two episodes of <em>The Studio</em> , which he co-created and executive produced, are set to premiere on March 26. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Studio — Official Teaser | Apple TV+" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ucgsmqxSJ1c?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> He plays Matt Remick, an executive who gets promoted to become the head of the fictional Continental Studios just as the movie industry is undergoing huge social and economic changes. Also starring in The Studio are the likes of Catherine O&#39;Hara, Kathryn Hahn, Ike Barinholtz and Chase Sui Wonders. Zac Efron, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">Martin Scorsese</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlize-theron">Charlize Theron</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zoe-kravitz">Zoë Kravitz</a> are among those guest-starring as themselves.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/seth-rogen-says-didnt-notice-when-james-franco-said-friendship-over-3837158">Seth Rogen says he didn&#39;t notice when James Franco said their friendship was over: “It really wasn&#39;t on my radar”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Wes Anderson's new film 'The Phoenician Scheme' is now coming out this summer https://www.nme.com/news/film/wes-andersons-new-film-the-phoenician-scheme-is-now-coming-out-this-summer-3837142?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wes-andersons-new-film-the-phoenician-scheme-is-now-coming-out-this-summerDamian Jones Tue, 11 Feb 2025 17:41:40 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3837142 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Wes Anderson" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The espionage comedy drama features an all star cast</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wes-andersons-new-film-the-phoenician-scheme-is-now-coming-out-this-summer-3837142">Wes Anderson&#39;s new film &#39;The Phoenician Scheme&#39; is now coming out this summer</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Wes Anderson" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_wesanderson_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/wes-anderson">Wes Anderson</a> is set to release his new film <em>The Phoenician Scheme</em> this summer.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wes-anderson-the-wonderful-story-of-henry-sugar-review-3492154">&#39;The Wonderful Story Of Henry Sugar&#39; review: Wes Anderson&#39;s magical Roald Dahl dalliance</a></strong></li></ul><p> The espionage comedy drama tells the story of a family business and stars Benicio del Toro as Zsa-zsa Korda, one of the richest men in Europe while Mia Threapleton plays his daughter and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-cera">Michael Cera</a> portrays her tutor.</p><p> The film features an all star cast which also includes <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hanks">Tom Hanks</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bill-murray">Bill Murray</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-cranston">Bryan Cranston</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/riz-ahmed">Riz Ahmed</a> , Jeffrey Wright, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scarlett-johansson">Scarlett Johansson</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/richard-ayoade">Richard Ayoade</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benedict-cumberbatch">Benedict Cumberbatch</a> .</p><p> According to <a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/wes-anderson-next-film-phoenician-scheme-release-date-focus-features-1236303296/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> , Focus Features has landed the domestic distribution rights to the movie, which is set to land in the US on a limited release on May 30 before a wide release on June 6. </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025_beniciodeltoro_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Benicio del Toro attends the opening ceremony during the 16th Film Festival Lumiere in Lyon on October 12, 2024 CREDIT: Stephane Cardinale – Corbis/Corbis via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Universal Pictures, Focus&#39; parent studio, is handling international distribution but a date is still to be set for a UK release.</p><p> In addition to directing <em>The Phoenician Scheme</em> , Anderson has also penned the script with the story co-written by Roman Coppola.</p><p> Elsewhere, the director <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wes-anderson-fantastic-mr-fox-unconventional-stop-motion-animation-3828529">recently opened up about his experience making 2009 stop-motion film <i>Fantastic Mr. Fox</i></a> , and the challenges he faced getting his crew on board with his approach to directing.</p><p> Speaking to <a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/features/wes-anderson-stop-motion-animation-master-class-1236267772/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAR1Avh9qqp0lejjQkUbitPPKlGJqpcOH2WgZGFjG2YxqXq5Nz4NNAKt91xg_aem_q43t2XhPKt8yXLIWv4wk6g"><i>Variety</i></a> at the time, Anderson said: “My ideas for how to go about making the movie were probably unconventional in ways I didn&#39;t realise … and so I ended up doing a lot of things that made it a lot more difficult.透明</p><p>Those “things” included unusual ways of capturing audio as well as redoing takes and lighting.</p><p> Anderson went on to tackle stop-motion again with 2018&#39;s <i>Isle Of Dogs</i> , which <i>NME</i> called his <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/isle-of-dogs-wes-anderson-film-review-2275948">“best work yet” in a five-star review</a> .</p><p> Meanwhile, the director <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wes-anderson-wins-first-oscar-of-career-doesnt-show-up-3599515">won his first Oscar</a> at the 2024 ceremony for Best Live Action Short Film for the Benedict Cumberbatch-starring <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wes-anderson-the-wonderful-story-of-henry-sugar-review-3492154"><i>The Wonderful Story Of Henry Sugar</i></a> – but was not present to accept the award.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wes-andersons-new-film-the-phoenician-scheme-is-now-coming-out-this-summer-3837142">Wes Anderson&#39;s new film &#39;The Phoenician Scheme&#39; is now coming out this summer</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
